- **Ongoing Announcement**: The PLCT (Programming Language and Compiler Technology) Lab at the Institute of Software, Chinese Academy of Sciences offers MoonBit internship opportunities for current students. Positions include **J139 MoonBit Application Development** and **J147 MoonBit RISC-V Compiler Development**. Features remote work with flexible hours. Interested students may refer to [PLCT Lab's Internship Openings](https://github.com/plctlab/weloveinterns/blob/master/open-internships.md).